note: Example 3 — step by 2 (even numbers 0 to 10).
print "Even numbers from 0 to 10.".
for i from 0 to 10 step 2 then
    print i.
end.

note: Countdown by 3 — descend using negative step stored in variable.
let countdown_step be 0 minus 3.
print "Countdown by 3 from 15 to 0.".
for i from 15 to 0 step countdown_step then
    print i.
end.
